## URL Structure and Navigation

The platform uses a hierarchical URL structure reflecting the product organization:
- `/analytics/` for core analytics features
- `/feature-experiment/` for experimentation capabilities
- `/sdks/` for development tools and instrumentation
- `/apis/` for programmatic access
- `/data/` for data management features
- `/admin/` for administrative functions

The navigation system uses injection-based organization with nav_title properties that group related functionality and maintain consistent user experience across the platform's extensive feature set.